<sec>
<st>
Philanthropy</st>

<p>

Louise Blouin MacBain founded the Louise T Blouin Foundation in 2005, with the aim of raising awareness about the role culture and creativity can play in resolving global issues. The foundation's website lists its two core aims as:</p>
<p>

<list>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

Encouraging a better understanding of foreign affairs and culture beyond borders through international cooperation, exchange and dialogue for the 21st century. </entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

Exploring the broader practical significance of creativity and the creative potential of the human brain.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%226%22])">6</ref></entry>
</list>
</p>
